
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Benifits";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/common_generallayout.cshtml";
}

<style>
    p {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    img {
        border-radius: 20px;
    }
</style>

<h1 class="text-center mt-4 text-info" style="font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">Benifits for you</h1>
<hr/>
<div class="container">
    <div data-aos="fade-up" class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img src="~/content/images/glob.jpg" width="100%" />

        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h2 class="text-primary text-center" style="font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif">Anywhere and anytime learning</h2>
            <p>
                With E-Education, learning is no longer confined to the four walls of a classroom. Whether you're at home, commuting, or traveling abroad — your learning continues.

                Our platform is accessible 24/7 across all devices, allowing you to take control of your educational journey. Set your own schedule, study at your own pace, and learn from anywhere in the world.

                Because true learning should fit into your life — not the other way around.

            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div data-aos="fade-up" class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h2 class="text-primary text-center" style="font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif">Wide range of Courses</h2>
            <p>
                We offer a diverse catalog of courses tailored to meet the evolving needs of students and professionals alike.
                <ul>
                    <li> Information Technology & Software Development</li>
                    <li> Business, Marketing & Entrepreneurship</li>
                    <li> Science, Mathematics & Academic Excellence</li>
                    <li> Communication, Language & Soft Skills</li>
                    <li>Creative Arts, Design & Personal Growth</li>
                </ul>

                Whether you're upskilling for your career, preparing for exams, or exploring new interests — we have the right course for you.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img src="~/content/images/books1.jpg" width="100%" style="height:300px;" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div data-aos="fade-up" class="row mt-3">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img src="~/content/images/hourg.jpeg" width="100%" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h2 class="text-primary text-center" style="font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">Learn at your own peace</h2>
            <p>
                At E-Education, we understand that everyone learns differently. That’s why our courses are designed to be 100% self-paced.

                No deadlines, no pressure — just the freedom to study when and how you want. Revisit lessons as many times as you need, pause when life gets busy, and continue exactly where you left off.

                Empower your learning journey with the flexibility you deserve.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

